  "text": "• In the United Kingdom, Germany and Denmark, PSM have self-regulatory mechanisms, the ex ante test. According to [CITATION_1] , empirical analyses show that accountability and transparency strategies improve organizations´ performance and governance. In the case of PSM, however, that is a generalization which requires a few observations.",
